						<div class="postbody">There was a <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=4020" class="postlink">topic about this</a> a while back.
<br />
<br />I believe that the most serious problems discussed were palette issues (the two characters use different palettes), slowdown (SMB already slows down with just one character, it would probably be much worse with two) and scrolling (what conditions would cause the camera to move or not).</div>

